{
  "stem": "7160.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So some guys, they knew at Birkenau there was no way you can survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To get anywhere else outside Birkenau, which is Auschwitz, Birkenau was about four miles different.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some people tried to go from the other line.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So in that time, they saw them, other people jumping in, you know, to the-- the-- the right side, where it's supposed to go to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We don't know where it was going to take it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I find out later it was Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that-- that-- and then the Germans start beating them up, you know, and threw the big German Shepherds on top of it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I find a chance, a time, and I sneak on the side, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went-- and I went with the-- with the healthy, strong people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I was not healthy and strong.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There-- now I don't know if I should say something about my cousin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Before I went to Warsaw, I was almost like a dead person.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was swelling everywhere with no food or anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had one cousin left, which his name was the same name as mines-- Albert Rose.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He-- he went to-- to Vienna, and he study.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He study to become some kind of-- I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was a young kid at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was about nine-- about nine or eight years older than me, I think.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and-- and he spoke German pretty good, because he went-- he spent some years in-- in Austria, and he learned the German language.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- he-- because he spoke the-- the language good, German, he had it very good.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was an interpreter, which they call them [GERMAN] in German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he-- to explain to the Greeks what the Germans say.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
